            }
          ]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                A jak jest z innymi punktami leżącymi na tym okręgu?\n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "pokaż dalej"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                Odległość każdego takiego punktu o współrzędnych \\(\\color{blue}{(x, y)}\\) od środka okręgu, \\(\\color{red}{S=(-3,2)}\\) także byłaby równa \\(5\\).\n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "flagged": true,
      "raw": "<table class=\"my_table_noborder narrow_table\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\\(\\color{blue}{A=(1,5)}\\):</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>\\((\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{1}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{(-3)}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2+(\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{5}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{2}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2\\)</td>\n<td>\\(=5^2\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\\(\\color{blue}{B=(-6,6)}\\):</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>\\((\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{-6}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{(-3)}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2+(\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{6}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{2}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2\\)</td>\n<td>\\(=5^2\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\\(\\color{blue}{C=(-7,-1)}\\):</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>\\((\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{-7}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{(-3)}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2+(\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{-1}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{2}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2\\)</td>\n<td>\\(=5^2\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"12\" style=\"text-align: left;\">czyli:</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\\(\\color{blue}{(x,y)}\\):</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>\\((\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{x}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{(-3)}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2+(\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{blue}{y}\\)</td>\n<td>\\(-\\)</td>\n<td>\\(\\color{red}{2}\\)</td>\n<td>\\()^2\\)</td>\n<td>\\(=5^2\\)</td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
      "reason": "table uses rowspan/colspan"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "pokaż dalej"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                I tak oto otrzymaliśmy <strong>równanie okręgu</strong> o środku w punkcie \\((-3,2)\\) i promieniu \\(5\\), \n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                czyli takie równanie, które spełniają punkty \\((x,y)\\) leżące na okręgu:\n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                \\[\n                (x-(-3))^2+(y-2)^2=5^2\n                \\]\n            "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                albo:\n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                \\[\n                (x+3)^2+(y-2)^2=25\n                \\]\n            "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "pokaż dalej"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                Bardziej ogólnie, <strong>równanie okręgu</strong> o środku w punkcie \\((a,b)\\) i promieniu \\(r\\) ma postać: \n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                \\[\n                (x-a)^2+(y-b)^2=r^2\n                \\]\n            "
    }
